      <title>费城数千名工人正在抗议每周工作五天的规定</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/07/11/nx-s1-5034972/thousands-of-philadelphia-city-workers-are-fighting-a-5-day-office-week-mandate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[费城市命令所有市政工作人员从 7 月 15 日起每周五天返回办公室。一名法官已经听取了工会关于推迟实施的请求的辩论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2024/07/11/nx-s1-5034972/thousands-of-philadelphia-city-workers-are-fighting-a-5-day-office-week-mandate</guid>
